The '''Spaceport Southeast II''' was the largest of ten [[Spaceport/Legends|spaceports]] on [[Bonadan/Legends|Bonadan]] and one of the most important in the [[Corporate Sector/Legends|Corporate Sector]]. The spaceport covered a larger area than many cities, although little of it extended above or below the planet's surface. There were numerous shipbuilding and refitting yards, dock facilities for barges and bulk freighters, an [[Security Police/Legends|Espo]] command center, an [[Authority Merchant Marine academy]], and the postmaster's headquarters. Added to that were passenger terminals, maintenance depots, ground transport installations, warehouses, and living and recreational arrangements for the thousands of [[Human/Legends|Humans]] and [[Alien/Legends|aliens]] who lived there or were just passing through.

